    &none               &mc_haha            &mc_term_exit       &mc_new_task        &none               &none               &mc_personal2       &mc_work            &mc_school          &none
    &none               &none               &none               &mc_new_task_enter  &none               &none               &mc_personal1       &none               &none               &none
                                            &none               &none               &none               &bootloader         &none               &none
